# NOTE: git does NOT support trailing comments on a pattern line — the whole
# line is taken as the pattern. Every comment here therefore sits on its own line.

# Helm
# vendored subchart tars from `helm dependency build`
charts/**/charts/
# regenerated by `helm dependency build`; kept out so a stale pin can never be
# committed (wrapper Chart.yaml files declare a floor, e.g. `>= 0.2.0`, and the
# file://../common dependency always resolves from this same checkout)
charts/**/Chart.lock
*.tgz

# Rendered / packaged output
/dist/
/output/
rendered.yaml

# Internal planning doc — not for the public repo
PLAN.md

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
.idea/
# Ignore the whole .vscode dir EXCEPT the shared settings.json. Note the form:
# `.vscode/*` (contents) not `.vscode/` (the dir) — git will not descend into a
# fully-excluded directory, so a negation for a file inside it would never match.
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json

# Secrets — belt-and-braces; this repo must never hold secret material
*.key
*.pem
secret*.yaml
*-secret.yaml
# ...but never exclude chart templates: an ExternalSecret *template* holds only
# references, no secret values, and some are named `*-secret.yaml`.
!charts/**/templates/**
